title: TOP 100 ALTERNATIVE ROCK SONGS
description:
As promised, I am back with my new compilation: TOP 100 ALTERNATIVE ROCK SONGS.  Here is my list of the Top 100 Alternative Rock songs made between approx 1996 - 2009.  

This type of music is hard to classify, really.  I've just grouped all of the alternative rock songs and included a few metal songs and a few alternative songs that seemed to be more like alternative rock.  If you're looking for songs by artists such as MxPx, Green Day, NoFX and the like, they'll be another upload entitled "Top 100 Alternative," although having already begun this list, it might need to be a top 250 list.  

Also, another notable thing about this torrent as opposed to some of my others is that every single file is mp3, which is an improvement over some of my previous torrents that had some mp4 and wma files.  This is my 5th list of the TOP 100 lists of all my different genres of music, and I'll have the rest posted shortly.  If you would like to see the others, here they are:
